import Nav from 'react-bootstrap/Nav';

function PillsExample() {
  return (
    <Nav variant="pills" defaultActiveKey="/home" style={{backgroundColor:"gray"}}>

    <Nav.Item>
        <bold>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="disabled" disabled style={{color:"orange",fontSize:"150%"
        ,fontStyle:"italic"}}> 
         Movies
        </Nav.Link></bold>
      </Nav.Item>

      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link to="/home">Active</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="link-1">Option 2</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>
      <Nav.Item>
        <Nav.Link eventKey="link-2">Option 3</Nav.Link>
      </Nav.Item>

    
    </Nav>
  );
}

export default PillsExample;
